# Core: Throttle Status + Daily Reset

### Get throttle status (admin)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/core/throttle/status
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}

### Reset daily counters for specific categories (requires manage_tenants)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/core/throttle/daily/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categories": ["send_whatsapp", "send_email"]
}

### Reset all categories defined by the tenant plan
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/core/throttle/daily/reset
Authorization: Bearer {{access}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}
